43:43.259 --> 43:44.540
Nabasa ko na rin nang sabay

43:46.540 --> 43:47.100
Okay lang

43:51.699 --> 43:52.339
Hindi ba't hindi ka

43:52.339 --> 43:53.619
Sa susunod na pre-trial coaching

43:53.619 --> 43:54.819
Wala akong oras para makinig

43:54.819 --> 43:55.619
Huwag na ulit

43:58.500 --> 43:59.460
Huwag na ulit

44:05.219 --> 44:06.020
Sige sige

44:06.619 --> 44:08.179
Huwag na ulit, huwag na ulit

