44:27.659 --> 44:29.100
Okay lang, isa na lang tingnan mo

44:29.580 --> 44:30.580
Kami na lang ang maghahati sa isa

44:35.219 --> 44:36.420
Dati wala namang butas pinipilit

44:36.580 --> 44:37.980
